title: Its About Time Episodes 01-03 DivX
description:
It's About Time

Two astronauts Mac, (Frank Aletter) and Hector (Jack Mullaney), accidentally break the speed of light, and get thrown back in time to prehistoric days. There, they have to adjust to living with a cave family led by Shadd (Imogene Coca) and Gronk (Joe E. Ross).

Episode 1: And Then I Wrote "Happy Birthday to You" (aired: 9/11/1966)
Episode 2: The Copper Caper (aired: 9/18/1966 )
Episode 3: The Initiation (aired: 9/25/1966)

This torrent replaces individual torrents for each episode. Episode 3 is the same file as before, and downloading can continue from this torrent on progress made from the previous one.
